data.description: Allow yourself to experience the beauty that is 181 Peters Rd. Nestled in the heart of Fayetteville, this charming property offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and traditional elegance, making it an ideal retreat for you and your loved ones. Step inside to discover a spacious and well-designed interior. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a welcoming atmosphere that's perfect for entertaining. You’re welcomed by a foyer entrance, soaring ceilings, archway openings, and pristine hardwood floors. Your kitchen is a true chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, freshly painted white cabinets, travertine backsplash, plenty of cabinet space, and ample natural lighting. Off of the kitchen, features your deck overlooking your serene secluded lot. Your master bedroom is on a split floor plan allowing for optimal privacy. The other two bedrooms on the main level offer ample space. The terrace level offers plenty of extra living space, featuring two open entertainment spaces, two spacious bedrooms, a bonus room, and a full bathroom. The home is situated on a 2.3 acre lot, perfect for gatherings and children or pets to roam! This home has been meticulously maintained and includes recent updates such as fresh interior paint, new carpet flooring on the terrace level, and modern fixtures throughout. This property's ideal location is minutes away from the Trilith neighborhood featuring several stores, restaurants, and attractions, as well as minutes away from Hartsfield- Jackson Atlanta Airport. Not to mention, In the highly desirable North Fayette School District. Come and experience this gem today!
